				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Lae'zel reacts to what she has just learned from the tiefling she questioned - and if the player didn't let her speak, she is mighty pissed about it, though her anger should be quite cool at this stage. Zaith'isk = ZAY-thisk. Kainyank = CANE-yank."
